  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To validate accuracy of the readings of noninvasive blood pressure (NIBP) module with
      sphygmomanometer as per the requirements of AAMI SP10:2002. This study is for adult and
      pediatric population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
